WEBVTT

01:40.380 --> 01:48.740
[You are My Fateful Love]
[EP01]

03:29.380 --> 03:30.739
[Well, well,]

03:31.380 --> 03:33.259
[Ms. Ruan.]

03:33.620 --> 03:34.419
[Guess who's]

03:34.419 --> 03:36.660
made it

03:36.660 --> 03:37.699
to her

03:38.139 --> 03:39.180
[one-year anniversary]

03:39.180 --> 03:40.340
[of writer's block?]

03:40.340 --> 03:41.539
[That's right,]

03:42.259 --> 03:43.019
[it's August 3rd,]

03:43.139 --> 03:45.539
[and still]

03:45.539 --> 03:46.500
no outline

03:48.060 --> 03:49.419
from you!

03:51.699 --> 03:52.940
[Chill,]

03:52.940 --> 03:54.060
Ms. Editor,

03:54.780 --> 03:56.739
I'm just going through some stuff

03:56.739 --> 03:58.019
at my parents' place.

03:58.460 --> 03:59.819
The outline's coming

04:00.380 --> 04:01.139
this month,

04:01.139 --> 04:02.819
like I promised.

04:04.100 --> 04:04.780
So...

04:04.780 --> 04:06.460
chosen a subject yet?

04:10.299 --> 04:11.060
Not exactly...

04:11.660 --> 04:13.100
Seriously? A whole year?

04:14.900 --> 04:16.419
You're finally making it

04:16.419 --> 04:18.019
as an author.

04:18.019 --> 04:19.419
Don't throw away all that momentum!

04:20.539 --> 04:21.419
I can't just

04:21.419 --> 04:22.699
make inspiration appear!

04:22.900 --> 04:24.379
[And it won't]

04:24.379 --> 04:25.580
[magically appear]

04:27.660 --> 04:28.859
[while you're holed up at home.]

04:28.859 --> 04:30.660
[Get out there]

04:30.660 --> 04:31.739
[and live!]

04:31.739 --> 04:32.979
[That's where]

04:33.220 --> 04:35.059
[stories come from!]

04:35.820 --> 04:38.260
[May 11. Perfect weather.]

04:39.220 --> 04:41.379
[Ran into him three times today.]

04:42.179 --> 04:42.939
[First one:]

04:43.499 --> 04:44.780
[me, clutching test papers,]

04:44.780 --> 04:45.700
[heading to the office.]

04:46.379 --> 04:47.499
[Him, getting the riot act]

04:47.499 --> 04:48.379
[from]

04:48.660 --> 04:50.260
[the guidance counselor]

04:51.299 --> 04:53.220
[with his buddies...]

04:53.460 --> 04:54.059
This is it!

04:55.499 --> 04:56.179
What's it?

04:57.100 --> 04:57.900
Did inspiration finally strike?

05:01.979 --> 05:04.580
High school. Secret crush!

05:05.780 --> 05:06.460
What's not to love?

05:16.340 --> 05:18.020
[Midnight.]

05:18.700 --> 05:19.660
[New Year's Eve.]

05:21.220 --> 05:23.299
[The school field was a sea of faces.]

05:24.660 --> 05:26.140
[After crushing on him]

05:27.140 --> 05:27.700
[forever,]

05:27.700 --> 05:29.220
[this was as close]

05:30.660 --> 05:33.419
[as she'd ever gotten...]

05:50.340 --> 05:51.379
11!

05:51.619 --> 05:56.739
10, 9, 8, 7, 6...

05:56.739 --> 05:58.179
[She'd managed to]

05:58.780 --> 05:59.419
4...

05:59.419 --> 06:01.100
[slip next to him.]

06:01.100 --> 06:03.939
2, 1...

06:12.419 --> 06:13.220
[Just as]

06:14.020 --> 06:15.580
[the fireworks exploded overhead,]

06:16.660 --> 06:18.020
[she felt his hand grab hers.]

06:54.859 --> 06:56.580
Sorry, wrong person...

07:38.499 --> 07:39.700
[She caught]

07:41.939 --> 07:43.780
[his embarrassed expression]

07:45.499 --> 07:46.580
[in the flickering light]

07:46.580 --> 07:47.580
[as he]

07:50.700 --> 07:51.700
[pulled away,]

07:53.260 --> 07:54.140
[apologizing]

07:58.100 --> 07:58.859
[for]

08:00.780 --> 08:01.539
[his mistake...]

08:27.700 --> 08:28.619
[Wrong person......]

08:30.419 --> 08:31.460
[Wrong person?]

08:33.580 --> 08:34.859
[But who was the right one?]

08:36.700 --> 08:37.739
[Was there]

08:38.900 --> 08:40.659
[already someone special in his life?]

08:57.979 --> 09:01.700
[You're not seriously writing]

09:02.300 --> 09:03.979
[a heartbreaking]

09:03.979 --> 09:05.259
[one-sided love story]

09:05.259 --> 09:06.659
[about him, are you?]

09:07.340 --> 09:08.180
[C'mon,]

09:08.540 --> 09:09.779
[people have enough drama in life,]

09:09.779 --> 09:11.379
[they don't need more heartbreak!]

09:12.019 --> 09:12.779
[Hey,]

09:13.420 --> 09:14.619
[I've already]

09:14.619 --> 09:16.220
[lived the sad ending.]

09:17.820 --> 09:19.379
[Time to give my character]

09:19.379 --> 09:20.379
[the romance I wish I'd had.]

09:33.220 --> 09:34.180
[After that...]

09:34.779 --> 09:36.019
[his heart]

09:36.820 --> 09:38.540
[was pounding like crazy,]

09:38.820 --> 09:40.340
[drowning out even the fireworks.]

09:41.779 --> 09:42.779
[Nobody knew...]

09:44.180 --> 09:44.979
[that "mistake"]

09:45.820 --> 09:47.340
[was his way of covering up the truth...]

10:36.060 --> 10:37.659
Here's the outline, Ms. Editor.

10:44.180 --> 10:45.220
This is going to...

10:45.739 --> 10:46.820
be your biggest hit yet.

10:50.979 --> 10:52.940
Well, nothing hits harder than

10:53.379 --> 10:54.739
writing your own story, huh?

10:58.379 --> 10:59.100
But

10:59.499 --> 11:00.739
seriously,

11:00.739 --> 11:02.100
what if

11:02.100 --> 11:02.779
he stumbles

11:03.540 --> 11:04.619
across it?

11:05.580 --> 11:06.220
I have

11:06.220 --> 11:07.499
thought it through.

11:07.619 --> 11:08.700
He barely knew

11:09.019 --> 11:10.420
I existed

11:10.420 --> 11:11.619
back then,

11:11.859 --> 11:12.739
it was

11:12.739 --> 11:13.979
totally

11:13.979 --> 11:14.820
one-sided.

11:14.940 --> 11:16.580
He'd never connect the dots.

11:17.019 --> 11:17.779
Besides,

11:18.180 --> 11:19.779
Mr. Too-Cool-For-School

11:19.779 --> 11:21.060
reading romance?

11:21.379 --> 11:22.460
As if!

11:24.139 --> 11:24.739
Good point...

11:32.499 --> 11:33.700
Hi Mom.

11:35.420 --> 11:36.899
Yeah, got it.

11:37.700 --> 11:38.340
Bye!

11:41.499 --> 11:42.340
Another...

11:42.340 --> 11:43.499
matchmaking attempt?

11:49.379 --> 11:51.060
Hold up,

11:51.739 --> 11:53.300
isn't that ringtone

11:54.180 --> 11:55.499
"After The Rain?"

11:55.499 --> 11:57.220
The one

11:57.220 --> 11:58.580
Xu Huaisong played at

11:58.580 --> 11:59.899
the school reunion?

12:00.060 --> 12:01.300
Stop overthinking it.

12:01.580 --> 12:03.060
The song just helps me

12:03.060 --> 12:03.779
tap into those memories

12:03.779 --> 12:04.659
for writing.

12:05.820 --> 12:06.739
Better be careful

12:07.180 --> 12:08.100
what kind of inspiration

12:08.100 --> 12:09.019
you're asking for!

12:37.420 --> 12:39.619
Want one explanation.

12:40.180 --> 12:40.979
You

12:41.220 --> 12:42.899
know or not?

12:43.499 --> 12:45.180
Listen, ma'am, I'm sorry.

12:45.379 --> 12:46.420
But the verdict is...

12:46.420 --> 12:47.100
What's the situation?

12:48.019 --> 12:48.619
She rented

12:48.619 --> 12:49.259
her property

12:49.259 --> 12:50.259
to some college students.

12:50.700 --> 12:51.420
They stopped paying

12:51.420 --> 12:53.060
and wouldn't leave,

12:53.460 --> 12:54.619
so she went there

12:54.619 --> 12:55.659
and shut off their utilities.

12:56.100 --> 12:57.139
Hired Jay to

12:57.139 --> 12:58.100
recover the rent,

12:58.779 --> 12:59.779
but now she's being countersued

12:59.779 --> 13:00.540
for illegal entry.

13:01.379 --> 13:02.300
Instead of getting paid,

13:02.700 --> 13:03.899
she might have to pay them.

13:04.700 --> 13:05.739
She's not taking it well.

13:07.180 --> 13:07.940
Jay,

13:08.619 --> 13:09.259
don't you dare leave!

13:09.259 --> 13:09.700
Ma'am...

13:09.700 --> 13:10.739
We're not done here!

13:10.739 --> 13:12.019
Let go of me!

13:12.340 --> 13:12.619
Ma'am!

13:12.619 --> 13:13.060
You can't bail on me!

13:13.060 --> 13:13.820
This is America,

13:13.820 --> 13:16.300
you have to obey the laws of the United States of America!

13:21.499 --> 13:23.540
It doesn't matter what country's laws

13:23.540 --> 13:24.379
we're talking about.

13:24.499 --> 13:26.420
If you lose, you lose.

13:26.700 --> 13:28.139
Finally, someone who gets it!

13:28.779 --> 13:29.379
Hey,

13:29.379 --> 13:31.180
this is ridiculous!

13:31.460 --> 13:32.499
How is it fair that

13:32.499 --> 13:34.340
I'm the one who has to pay?

13:34.540 --> 13:35.820
Courts follow the law,

13:36.060 --> 13:36.979
not what seems fair.

13:38.659 --> 13:40.019
So I actually

13:40.499 --> 13:41.739
have to pay them?

13:42.060 --> 13:42.619
Yes,

13:45.940 --> 13:47.060
but first, I need honest answers

13:47.300 --> 13:48.779
to two questions.

13:49.659 --> 13:50.340
When exactly

13:51.300 --> 13:52.700
did the lease

13:52.700 --> 13:53.499
terminate,

13:53.779 --> 13:55.300
and which months of rent

13:55.300 --> 13:56.420
are you trying to collect?

13:56.739 --> 13:58.060
The lease ended in February.

13:58.499 --> 13:59.820
We never renewed

13:59.899 --> 14:00.859
in writing,

14:01.100 --> 14:02.940
just verbal.

14:03.259 --> 14:04.460
But they haven't paid

14:04.700 --> 14:06.540
since February!

14:07.060 --> 14:08.580
And you knew

14:08.580 --> 14:09.859
they were still occupying

14:10.420 --> 14:11.820
the property

14:12.060 --> 14:13.019
after the lease expired?

14:13.019 --> 14:14.100
Yes, I did.

14:16.180 --> 14:18.420
Are you completely certain about that?

14:19.779 --> 14:20.460
Oh...

14:23.899 --> 14:25.180
perhaps I didn't know...

14:26.499 --> 14:27.379
If you weren't aware,

14:27.899 --> 14:28.659
then

14:28.659 --> 14:30.100
we're dealing with

14:30.659 --> 14:32.300
unlawful entry

14:32.300 --> 14:33.060
and

14:33.060 --> 14:34.619
unauthorized use

14:34.619 --> 14:35.499
of

14:35.499 --> 14:36.659
private property.

14:37.540 --> 14:38.300
The implications

14:38.379 --> 14:39.540
are clear.

14:40.420 --> 14:42.220
This is brilliant!

14:42.220 --> 14:43.100
What a

14:43.100 --> 14:44.420
game-changer!

14:45.259 --> 14:46.220
While the law is rigid,

14:46.739 --> 14:47.580
its application is flexible.

14:48.139 --> 14:48.820
Huaisong,

14:49.259 --> 14:51.779
are you sure that you wanna be meddling in my affairs?

14:51.859 --> 14:53.100
This is my case.

14:53.100 --> 14:55.019
I guess we have different definitions

14:55.019 --> 14:56.300
of the word "meddle."

14:56.779 --> 14:57.899
And in my view,

14:58.019 --> 14:59.580
I'm cleaning up your mess.

15:01.379 --> 15:04.220
Listen, just because you have some type of "big win rate,"

15:04.979 --> 15:06.779
doesn't mean you can be an arrogant prick!

15:11.180 --> 15:13.300
I'll take that as a compliment.

15:13.540 --> 15:14.979
And just DO YOUR JOB!

15:21.499 --> 15:22.220
I'm sorry, ma'am,

15:23.540 --> 15:24.460
let's go to my office

15:24.460 --> 15:25.580
so we can talk more privately

15:25.580 --> 15:26.499
and I can help you.

15:36.899 --> 15:37.460
Boss,

15:37.820 --> 15:38.779
Jay

15:39.019 --> 15:40.180
was fuming!

15:40.580 --> 15:41.979
Served him right!

15:43.259 --> 15:44.340
His reaction

15:44.340 --> 15:45.379
is irrelevant.

15:45.739 --> 15:46.779
The firm's reputation

15:47.540 --> 15:48.619
is

15:48.820 --> 15:50.100
what matters.

15:52.259 --> 15:53.540
You really need to

15:53.540 --> 15:54.379
ease up on cola.

15:57.379 --> 15:57.940
Oh,

15:59.300 --> 16:00.220
the client from

16:00.220 --> 16:01.379
that criminal case

16:01.580 --> 16:02.460
is still pushing to

16:02.460 --> 16:03.420
have you

16:03.619 --> 16:04.499
represent them.

16:04.499 --> 16:06.420
I don't take criminal cases, period.

16:10.300 --> 16:11.619
It's been so long since...

16:12.340 --> 16:13.300
Some wounds

16:13.580 --> 16:15.019
don't heal with time.

16:20.259 --> 16:20.859
OK.

16:36.259 --> 16:37.300
[Ms. Lily Vale,]

16:37.300 --> 16:38.100
[your new novel]

16:38.100 --> 16:39.540
["Whispers of the Heart"]

16:39.619 --> 16:40.460
is already

16:40.460 --> 16:41.979
a chart-topper,

16:42.300 --> 16:43.700
[and we're hearing about]

16:43.700 --> 16:45.139
[potential screen adaptations.]

16:45.619 --> 16:46.899
[Any exclusive news]

16:46.899 --> 16:48.100
[you can share?]

16:49.859 --> 16:50.540
[First,]

16:50.739 --> 16:51.899
[I'm incredibly thankful]

16:51.899 --> 16:53.180
[for all the support.]

16:53.540 --> 16:55.259
This story explores

16:55.259 --> 16:56.379
mutual secret crushes in high school.

16:57.619 --> 16:58.700
I hope readers

16:58.700 --> 16:59.779
fall in love with it.

17:00.139 --> 17:01.379
As for adaptation news,

17:02.379 --> 17:03.300
you'll be

17:03.460 --> 17:04.340
the first to know

17:04.340 --> 17:05.259
when there's something to announce.

17:05.300 --> 17:05.820
Check this out,

17:05.820 --> 17:07.100
possible plagiarism...

17:07.979 --> 17:09.060
The evidence is mounting...

17:09.700 --> 17:10.499
Check the plagiarism checker...

17:12.459 --> 17:12.899
Hey,

17:12.899 --> 17:13.699
something's fishy...

17:14.580 --> 17:14.939
Well...

17:16.219 --> 17:16.699
Thank you.

17:16.699 --> 17:17.500
Ms. Lily Vale,

17:17.780 --> 17:18.780
what's your take on

17:19.500 --> 17:20.859
the online accusations

17:20.980 --> 17:22.179
about

17:22.179 --> 17:23.379
your work's authenticity?

17:23.379 --> 17:25.179
The New Year's scene

17:25.179 --> 17:26.459
matches

17:26.459 --> 17:27.899
"The Poet's" work

17:27.899 --> 17:28.939
almost word for word

17:28.939 --> 17:29.699
the scene, dialogue, character thoughts.

17:30.060 --> 17:31.100
How do you

17:31.100 --> 17:32.379
explain this?

17:32.740 --> 17:34.260
Are potential producers

17:34.260 --> 17:35.659
aware of these issues?

17:36.300 --> 17:37.939
Does your prolific output

17:38.179 --> 17:40.139
suggest previous works

17:40.139 --> 17:41.100
might also be questionable?

17:41.780 --> 17:42.580
Your thoughts on

17:42.580 --> 17:43.500
the current controversy?

17:44.379 --> 17:46.379
Like all of you,

17:46.379 --> 17:47.659
I'm just learning about this now.

17:48.219 --> 17:48.939
Please

17:48.939 --> 17:50.020
give me some time,

17:50.020 --> 17:51.340
I will address these concerns

17:51.699 --> 17:53.100
and provide a proper explanation.

17:53.820 --> 17:54.500
Thank you.

17:55.939 --> 17:56.699
Are you refusing

17:56.939 --> 17:58.500
to address the allegations?

17:58.619 --> 17:59.179
Stop! Please!

17:59.179 --> 17:59.939
We need answers!

18:00.219 --> 18:01.100
Just one statement,

18:01.100 --> 18:01.500
please!

18:01.500 --> 18:02.500
Ms. Lily Vale,

18:02.500 --> 18:03.060
please!

18:03.139 --> 18:03.580
Please stop!

18:03.580 --> 18:04.459
We need answers!

18:04.459 --> 18:05.260
Please!

18:05.379 --> 18:06.459
Ms. Lily Vale!

18:06.899 --> 18:07.980
Please, Ms. Lily Vale!

18:08.219 --> 18:08.699
Ms. Lily Vale...

18:08.699 --> 18:09.100
As a writer known for

18:09.100 --> 18:10.060
original work for six years...

18:10.060 --> 18:10.580
Mingying,

18:10.619 --> 18:11.619
what the hell is going on?

18:11.740 --> 18:12.980
[They found matching details]

18:12.980 --> 18:14.459
[between your work]

18:14.459 --> 18:15.139
[and "Her Smiling Eyes"]

18:15.139 --> 18:16.300
[too many to be coincidental.]

18:16.899 --> 18:17.419
Is this running

18:17.419 --> 18:18.540
an admission?

18:18.540 --> 18:19.820
It's been six years,

18:19.820 --> 18:20.580
why throw it all away now?

18:20.580 --> 18:21.260
Ms. Lily Vale...

18:21.740 --> 18:22.500
Ms. Lily Vale,

18:22.540 --> 18:23.340
your comment...

18:23.459 --> 18:24.619
Just one answer,

18:24.619 --> 18:25.580
please?

18:26.300 --> 18:27.459
Ms. Lily Vale...

18:27.939 --> 18:29.740
Ms. Lily Vale! Ms. Lily Vale!

18:30.219 --> 18:30.980
Ms. Lily Vale!

18:34.459 --> 18:35.459
Check out the plagiarism checker.

18:46.419 --> 18:47.500
They beat us

18:47.500 --> 18:47.859
to publication

18:47.859 --> 18:48.820
by weeks.

18:48.820 --> 18:49.820
Same story,

18:50.100 --> 18:51.219
just flipped perspectives,

18:51.580 --> 18:53.060
yours from her eyes,

18:53.219 --> 18:54.619
theirs from his.

18:56.540 --> 18:57.580
[Sorry, wrong person...]

18:58.139 --> 18:59.060
[That "mistake" was ]

18:59.179 --> 19:00.699
[his way of covering up the truth...]

19:00.939 --> 19:02.020
["Whispers of the Heart."]

19:02.820 --> 19:03.580
[I lied.]

19:03.580 --> 19:04.340
[You were the one...]

19:05.179 --> 19:06.300
["Her Smiling Eyes."]

19:07.139 --> 19:08.340
The internal monologues

19:08.340 --> 19:09.340
are identical!

19:22.100 --> 19:22.740
Got it!

19:23.179 --> 19:24.060
Got her profile.

19:26.379 --> 19:27.740
"Back to campus..."

19:28.459 --> 19:29.659
She's a student.

19:30.300 --> 19:31.699
I need to reach out to her.

19:32.020 --> 19:32.780
Yes, get to the bottom

19:32.780 --> 19:34.260
of these similarities.

19:36.100 --> 19:37.300
[While I can prove]

19:37.300 --> 19:37.859
["Whispers"]

19:38.100 --> 19:39.820
[is my original work,]

19:40.219 --> 19:41.699
[I'm concerned about]

19:42.020 --> 19:43.459
[our stories']

19:43.540 --> 19:44.659
[striking similarities.]

19:45.020 --> 19:45.939
[I'm deeply puzzled]

19:45.939 --> 19:47.219
[by this.]

19:47.540 --> 19:49.260
[I'd appreciate]

19:49.500 --> 19:50.500
[discussing this with you.]

19:53.060 --> 19:54.379
Ten years of

19:54.379 --> 19:55.659
nursing a broken heart,

19:56.020 --> 19:56.859
and now

19:57.260 --> 19:58.340
when you finally

19:58.340 --> 19:59.419
write your pain into fiction,

19:59.540 --> 20:00.859
they call you a copycat.

20:01.020 --> 20:02.340
It's not a fiction!

20:06.179 --> 20:06.820
Well...

20:08.300 --> 20:09.659
I guess

20:10.659 --> 20:11.540
it sort of is...

20:19.780 --> 20:20.659
Sweetie,

20:21.060 --> 20:21.899
about that nice boy

20:21.899 --> 20:22.939
from yesterday,

20:22.939 --> 20:24.300
he's free tomorrow.

20:24.659 --> 20:26.100
Let me send his picture first,

20:26.100 --> 20:26.580
alright?

20:26.740 --> 20:28.060
If you think he's cute...

20:28.060 --> 20:30.060
Mom, I'm in the middle of something...

20:30.500 --> 20:32.139
Always something!

20:32.260 --> 20:33.340
When aren't you busy?

20:33.459 --> 20:34.419
You can have both

20:34.419 --> 20:35.340
a career AND a love life.

20:35.780 --> 20:37.060
According to Mrs. Li,

20:37.060 --> 20:37.980
he's

20:37.980 --> 20:39.459
[very successful.]

20:39.859 --> 20:40.780
[And listen,]

20:40.780 --> 20:42.219
he's a lawyer!

20:42.340 --> 20:43.740
[I'll send his photo.]

20:43.740 --> 20:44.859
If you like what you see,

20:44.859 --> 20:45.780
meet him tomorrow.

20:45.780 --> 20:46.899
I really think he's the one.

20:47.219 --> 20:47.699
Fine.

20:56.300 --> 20:56.980
Hello,

20:58.699 --> 21:00.060
Liu Mao,

21:00.060 --> 21:00.659
Zhikun Law Firm.

21:01.699 --> 21:02.500
My card.

21:03.899 --> 21:04.459
Ruan Yu,

21:05.219 --> 21:06.020
pleased to meet you.

21:06.459 --> 21:07.300
Hello, hi.

21:07.820 --> 21:08.780
Mr. Liu,

21:08.780 --> 21:10.260
we must be around the same age.

21:10.780 --> 21:12.500
Making partner

21:12.500 --> 21:13.980
so young,

21:14.379 --> 21:15.139
that's quite

21:15.139 --> 21:16.340
an achievement.

21:16.540 --> 21:17.100
Nah,

21:17.980 --> 21:18.939
I'm flattered.

21:19.179 --> 21:20.300
To be honest,

21:20.300 --> 21:21.300
we have four partners.

21:22.020 --> 21:24.459
I'm just the working partner.

21:24.459 --> 21:25.340
Pretty low on the totem pole!

21:25.939 --> 21:27.100
We have

21:27.100 --> 21:28.740
a senior advisor overseas,

21:28.740 --> 21:29.699
he's the real star.

21:30.980 --> 21:32.139
Does overseas mean

21:32.619 --> 21:34.179
he doesn't do the actual work?

21:34.300 --> 21:36.020
No, no,

21:36.419 --> 21:37.060
I mean,

21:37.060 --> 21:38.580
he practices law there.

21:38.939 --> 21:40.740
The financial backing

21:40.740 --> 21:41.899
is important work too...

21:48.699 --> 21:50.300
[Talk about timing...]

21:53.260 --> 21:54.340
Sorry, Ms. Ruan.

21:54.340 --> 21:56.100
I don't mix work with dates.

21:56.459 --> 21:57.859
I don't mind work talk.

21:57.899 --> 21:58.939
No, really.

21:58.939 --> 21:59.740
I'm strict about

21:59.740 --> 22:00.580
separating work

22:00.580 --> 22:01.580
and personal life.

22:03.100 --> 22:04.139
Actually,

22:04.659 --> 22:05.980
I really need your professional input.

22:16.300 --> 22:17.419
Sorry to turn lunch

22:17.619 --> 22:18.580
into a consultation,

22:18.580 --> 22:19.619
Mr. Liu.

22:19.780 --> 22:20.619
It's fine!

22:20.859 --> 22:22.980
I actually believe in

22:23.780 --> 22:25.379
drawing from

22:25.379 --> 22:26.899
life experiences for work.

22:26.899 --> 22:29.540
They're two sides of

22:29.699 --> 22:31.219
the same coin.

22:34.139 --> 22:35.219
So, Mr. Liu,

22:35.500 --> 22:36.419
what would you recommend

22:36.419 --> 22:37.619
in my case?

22:39.699 --> 22:40.619
From what you've

22:40.619 --> 22:41.780
told me,

22:41.780 --> 22:43.139
since "The Poet"

22:43.139 --> 22:44.820
published her work online first,

22:45.260 --> 22:45.859
legally,

22:46.179 --> 22:47.340
you can't claim plagiarism.

22:48.780 --> 22:50.060
And since she

22:50.179 --> 22:51.379
hasn't made

22:51.740 --> 22:53.100
any public appearances

22:53.100 --> 22:54.300
or statements,

22:54.300 --> 22:56.100
we can't build a case

22:56.100 --> 22:56.740
against her.

22:57.459 --> 22:58.139
As for

22:58.139 --> 22:59.300
going after everyone

22:59.300 --> 23:00.419
who left comments online...

23:00.980 --> 23:01.580
sure,

23:01.699 --> 23:02.740
it's technically

23:02.740 --> 23:03.820
possible,

23:03.820 --> 23:04.659
but I really

23:04.859 --> 23:06.020
wouldn't go down that road.

23:06.780 --> 23:07.580
It'll be nothing but

23:07.580 --> 23:08.659
a waste of time and energy,

23:10.060 --> 23:10.859
Got it.

23:12.060 --> 23:12.820
Mr. Liu,

23:12.939 --> 23:13.899
any recommendations

23:13.899 --> 23:14.699
for me?

23:16.139 --> 23:17.540
Let's watch and wait.

23:17.540 --> 23:18.619
See what "The Poet"

23:18.619 --> 23:19.780
is planning.

23:25.179 --> 23:25.980
Excuse me.

23:27.540 --> 23:28.219
Mr. Liu,

23:28.219 --> 23:29.100
something urgent came up.

23:29.100 --> 23:30.100
I have to leave.

23:30.300 --> 23:30.859
Thank you

23:30.859 --> 23:31.820
for your insights.

23:31.820 --> 23:32.939
Let's meet again sometime?

23:35.260 --> 23:36.260
Lunch is on me,

23:36.300 --> 23:37.740
consider it consultation fee.

23:37.740 --> 23:39.139
I'll transfer more if needed.

23:39.540 --> 23:40.540
That's unnecessary.

23:40.780 --> 23:42.179
When would you like to meet again?

23:42.179 --> 23:43.419
Once we have someone to sue.

23:45.340 --> 23:46.699
He thinks we should wait for

23:46.699 --> 23:47.899
"The Poet" to make a move.

23:48.980 --> 23:49.859
[Is he any good?]

23:50.899 --> 23:52.060
Not sure,

23:52.219 --> 23:52.859
but he made

23:52.859 --> 23:54.100
a valid point:

23:54.540 --> 23:55.899
everything

23:56.179 --> 23:56.939
depends on

23:56.939 --> 23:58.179
"The Poet's" stance.

23:58.379 --> 23:59.459
Maybe she'll

23:59.459 --> 24:00.459
clear things up.

24:00.899 --> 24:01.939
[You should be happy]

24:01.939 --> 24:03.379
if she doesn't sue you.

24:03.379 --> 24:04.139
Expecting her to

24:04.139 --> 24:05.340
defend you is wishful thinking.

24:06.980 --> 24:08.340
I just need her to believe

24:08.340 --> 24:09.419
it's original.

24:10.379 --> 24:11.300
[Let's just wait...]

24:11.419 --> 24:12.219
Hold up,

24:13.219 --> 24:14.619
"The Poet" just came online.

24:19.219 --> 24:20.699
Some writer

24:20.980 --> 24:21.899
she is!

24:21.899 --> 24:23.020
No integrity whatsoever!

24:24.020 --> 24:24.859
What writer?

24:28.939 --> 24:30.179
[I deny all plagiarism claims.]

24:30.659 --> 24:31.020
[Regarding]

24:31.020 --> 24:32.219
[the similarities between]

24:32.219 --> 24:33.619
["Whispers"]

24:33.939 --> 24:35.300
[and "Her Smiling Eyes,"]

24:35.540 --> 24:36.699
[I've reached out]

24:36.699 --> 24:37.899
[to "The Poet"]

24:38.060 --> 24:38.939
[and await her response.]

24:39.540 --> 24:40.540
[I'll provide]

24:40.740 --> 24:42.260
[a complete explanation soon.]

24:43.419 --> 24:43.899
[God knows,]

24:43.899 --> 24:45.219
[this story of secret love]

24:45.580 --> 24:46.580
[comes from]

24:46.580 --> 24:47.500
[my own high school days.]

24:48.939 --> 24:50.179
Her high school days?

24:51.260 --> 24:52.540
She's quite the actress.

24:52.939 --> 24:54.340
That's not her story to tell!

24:58.100 --> 24:59.219
This weighs a ton...

25:14.699 --> 25:15.780
Huaisong's phone...

25:30.859 --> 25:32.300
[Tonight's fireworks were amazing.]

25:33.179 --> 25:34.139
[And...]

25:35.060 --> 25:35.859
[I lied.]

25:36.780 --> 25:37.619
[You were the one...]

25:38.540 --> 25:39.500
[Happy New Year!]

25:46.260 --> 25:47.219
Oh my god,

25:50.139 --> 25:51.100
there's tons of these...

25:52.219 --> 25:52.699
So,

25:52.699 --> 25:54.260
during the move,

25:54.260 --> 25:55.899
you found these recordings of

25:55.899 --> 25:57.139
your brother

25:57.139 --> 25:58.740
talking about his crush...

25:59.980 --> 26:01.379
KEEP IT DOWN!

26:04.459 --> 26:05.619
From the other class...

26:07.219 --> 26:07.980
So...

26:08.179 --> 26:11.300
this was your brother's real story?

26:11.300 --> 26:11.820
Yeah.

26:11.820 --> 26:13.260
If this is Lily Vale's story too,

26:13.540 --> 26:14.459
and both stories have

26:14.699 --> 26:16.179
the same details...

26:18.020 --> 26:19.419
Could it mean...

26:23.939 --> 26:24.740
Mean what?

26:26.100 --> 26:27.740
Wait, are you suggesting...

26:28.419 --> 26:30.459
Lily Vale was my brother's classmate?

26:32.500 --> 26:34.300
And they had

26:34.459 --> 26:35.379
secret crushes

26:35.379 --> 26:36.300
on each other?

26:36.619 --> 26:37.459
No. No way.

26:37.459 --> 26:38.060
That's too much

26:38.060 --> 26:38.939
of a coincidence!

26:39.060 --> 26:39.580
Nah...

26:41.820 --> 26:43.300
Check this out,

26:43.580 --> 26:44.139
see,

26:44.540 --> 26:46.580
all her food posts

26:46.580 --> 26:47.780
are local dishes.

26:48.100 --> 26:48.780
She must be

26:48.780 --> 26:49.740
from here.

26:51.540 --> 26:53.459
You're actually right...

26:56.060 --> 26:57.699
This is crazy!

27:02.820 --> 27:04.540
Hey dude,

27:04.780 --> 27:06.020
your brain

27:06.300 --> 27:07.699
might be slow

27:07.699 --> 27:08.540
for math,

27:08.939 --> 27:10.379
but it's NASCAR-fast for drama!

27:12.939 --> 27:13.859
THANKS FOR THAT!

27:25.580 --> 27:26.379
OMG,

27:27.020 --> 27:29.459
your hair is

27:29.659 --> 27:31.020
everything today!

27:31.980 --> 27:32.899
And

27:32.899 --> 27:33.859
that complexion?

27:33.859 --> 27:35.139
Flawless!

27:35.939 --> 27:36.820
And this uniform...

27:37.340 --> 27:38.659
I mean, same as always,

27:38.659 --> 27:40.419
but today? You're killing it!

27:41.459 --> 27:41.899
And...

27:41.899 --> 27:44.100
that jaw could cut glass!

27:44.379 --> 27:45.340
That profile!

27:45.580 --> 27:46.619
Even

27:46.699 --> 27:48.020
the popular guys

27:48.020 --> 27:48.980
would be jealous!

27:49.139 --> 27:50.699
They'd literally die

27:50.780 --> 27:51.580
of jealousy...

27:51.580 --> 27:52.179
Enough!

27:53.500 --> 27:54.740
You're only nice

27:54.740 --> 27:55.899
when you want something!

27:56.379 --> 27:58.139
Aren't we besties?

27:59.899 --> 28:01.300
That depends on

28:01.300 --> 28:02.659
your next words.

28:02.899 --> 28:05.659
With your connections,

28:05.659 --> 28:07.060
you could totally find out

28:07.459 --> 28:08.459
who Lily Vale

28:08.459 --> 28:09.780
really is...

28:13.939 --> 28:14.740
I know you're

28:14.740 --> 28:16.540
THE BEST BESTIE EVER!

28:16.980 --> 28:17.859
Hold up!

28:18.260 --> 28:19.500
Three months of math homework!

28:28.060 --> 28:28.939
Fine, one month...

28:34.580 --> 28:35.340
Deal!

28:36.100 --> 28:37.020
Buy me one Boba.

28:49.780 --> 28:51.179
Yeah, OK,

28:51.459 --> 28:51.939
perfect.

28:53.740 --> 28:54.419
Thanks!

28:54.419 --> 28:55.980
I'll buy you crayfish.

28:56.980 --> 28:57.780
What'd you find?

28:57.859 --> 28:58.419
Tell me!

29:10.500 --> 29:11.740
Ruan Yu?

29:13.859 --> 29:15.260
That's your Lily Vale.

29:25.899 --> 29:28.100
Dude, one more thing,

29:29.060 --> 29:29.939
go to the school art gallery

29:29.939 --> 29:30.619
with me?

29:31.820 --> 29:32.500
Why there?

29:34.540 --> 29:35.859
Need to confirm something.

29:49.139 --> 29:50.219
Should be here...

29:51.379 --> 29:52.100
the piano...

29:54.179 --> 29:55.100
Dude, c'mon,

29:55.780 --> 29:56.619
help me move it.

29:57.820 --> 29:58.540
Think

29:58.740 --> 30:00.020
they've repainted

30:00.100 --> 30:01.780
the wall?

30:01.780 --> 30:02.899
Nah,

30:03.139 --> 30:04.139
school's too cheap.

30:05.540 --> 30:06.100
Let me.

30:12.060 --> 30:13.780
In her story,

30:14.300 --> 30:17.859
she wrote her initials

30:17.859 --> 30:19.379
on the wall

30:19.780 --> 30:21.859
where he practiced piano...

30:25.179 --> 30:26.179
What are we searching for?

30:26.619 --> 30:27.419
I'll look too.

30:37.219 --> 30:38.219
Got it!

30:42.419 --> 30:45.020
RY...

30:45.899 --> 30:47.020
X...

30:47.419 --> 30:50.580
loves... Xu Huaishi (XHS)...

30:52.659 --> 30:53.419
Who's RY?

30:53.619 --> 30:54.659
Tell me.

30:55.419 --> 30:56.540
Ren Yi from Class A?

30:56.540 --> 30:57.859
Ran Yu from Class E?

30:58.219 --> 30:59.060
Don't tell me it's

30:59.060 --> 30:59.899
Fatso Rong from 10th grade...

30:59.899 --> 31:01.139
Huaishi, aren't you

31:01.379 --> 31:02.580
a bit old for that kid?

31:02.939 --> 31:04.020
Ruan Yu...

31:04.619 --> 31:06.780
loves Xu Huaisong...

31:08.500 --> 31:09.740
Oh my god,

31:10.100 --> 31:12.820
this is beautiful!

31:13.939 --> 31:14.740
What are you doing here?

31:14.740 --> 31:15.580
Which class are you from?

31:15.859 --> 31:16.540
Step out!

31:20.980 --> 31:23.020
Your genius plan worked great!

31:38.939 --> 31:40.659
Did you pull an all-nighter?

31:43.340 --> 31:44.060
Something's off.

31:45.459 --> 31:46.659
Too many matches...

31:48.060 --> 31:49.060
Remember

31:49.139 --> 31:50.260
that plant craze

31:50.899 --> 31:52.260
at school?

31:52.300 --> 31:54.260
Everyone growing those

31:54.939 --> 31:55.939
mini gardens,

31:55.939 --> 31:56.740
four-leaf clovers,

31:56.740 --> 31:57.899
mimosa plants...

31:58.139 --> 31:59.300
I experimented with

31:59.300 --> 31:59.899
different seeds though.

31:59.899 --> 32:00.699
Ring any bells?

32:00.939 --> 32:01.659
Yeah,

32:02.020 --> 32:03.219
you managed

32:03.219 --> 32:04.659
sunflowers and

32:04.659 --> 32:05.659
lavender together.

32:06.219 --> 32:06.780
Total garden influencer

32:06.780 --> 32:08.219
before Instagram existed...

32:08.659 --> 32:09.419
Over here!

32:11.060 --> 32:12.500
Look at her version,

32:13.980 --> 32:14.740
quick!

32:14.740 --> 32:15.980
What? What is it?

32:16.060 --> 32:16.780
Look here:

32:17.300 --> 32:17.980
That weekend,

32:17.980 --> 32:19.219
she left campus

32:19.219 --> 32:20.219
with her mini garden,

32:20.300 --> 32:21.500
where sunflowers

32:21.500 --> 32:22.619
and lavender bloomed together...

32:23.020 --> 32:24.260
It's exactly the same!

32:24.260 --> 32:26.020
- Right?
- This is insane...

32:26.020 --> 32:27.379
Who could've done this?

32:28.300 --> 32:29.859
The site's taking down

32:29.859 --> 32:30.780
your story at 9

32:30.780 --> 32:31.699
if this

32:31.699 --> 32:32.980
isn't resolved, right?

32:32.980 --> 32:33.939
What time is it?

32:40.939 --> 32:41.619
Hello,

32:41.780 --> 32:43.939
I deeply apologize for the trouble.

32:44.459 --> 32:45.939
"Her Smiling Eyes"

32:45.939 --> 32:47.780
wasn't my original work.

32:48.139 --> 32:49.459
I based it on an outline

32:49.459 --> 32:50.699
I purchased.

32:51.379 --> 32:52.060
I apologize for

32:52.300 --> 32:53.740
infringing on your rights.

32:54.060 --> 32:55.939
I'll explain publicly,

32:56.219 --> 32:57.619
apologize,

32:57.740 --> 32:58.899
remove the story,

32:59.139 --> 33:00.459
and delete my account.

33:00.859 --> 33:03.060
Here's my proposed statement

33:03.379 --> 33:04.459
for your review.

33:05.699 --> 33:07.139
Someone sold your outline!

33:08.179 --> 33:09.780
Who else saw it

33:09.780 --> 33:10.740
besides me?

33:10.820 --> 33:11.820
No one...

33:14.459 --> 33:15.219
The USB!

33:15.659 --> 33:16.939
At the café,

33:16.939 --> 33:17.899
when we discussed the outline,

33:17.899 --> 33:18.980
I brought a USB.

33:19.219 --> 33:20.060
Did you forget it there?

33:28.139 --> 33:29.219
What do you think?

33:30.219 --> 33:31.459
This is going to...

33:31.859 --> 33:32.939
be your biggest hit yet.

33:33.300 --> 33:33.899
Right, they say

33:33.899 --> 33:35.340
they purchased an outline...

33:36.540 --> 33:37.060
Give me a sec.

33:37.060 --> 33:37.740
Where you going?

33:38.139 --> 33:39.780
Checking the café.

33:39.859 --> 33:40.939
Could you search your place?

33:41.219 --> 33:41.899
OK, but...

33:42.179 --> 33:43.139
I know, I'll ask about

33:43.139 --> 33:44.179
her outline's source.

33:46.859 --> 33:47.780
Yes, yes,

33:47.780 --> 33:48.899
we're sorting it out...

33:51.980 --> 33:52.899
Here's your order.

33:54.260 --> 33:54.859
Thanks!

33:56.859 --> 33:58.500
She's asking where I got the outline.

33:59.580 --> 34:00.419
Now what...

34:00.419 --> 34:01.540
What do I say?

34:01.540 --> 34:02.540
I told you

34:02.540 --> 34:03.820
this was a bad idea!

34:04.260 --> 34:05.580
Maybe just tell her the truth?

34:06.939 --> 34:07.939
That's even worse!

34:08.300 --> 34:09.340
If she finds out,

34:09.419 --> 34:10.179
my brother will

34:10.179 --> 34:11.139
know too.

34:11.139 --> 34:12.100
If he learns

34:12.100 --> 34:12.780
I turned his...

34:13.139 --> 34:14.699
private thoughts into a story...

34:14.939 --> 34:15.419
He...

34:15.540 --> 34:17.219
He'll literally end me!

34:17.219 --> 34:18.339
He's a lawyer,

34:19.219 --> 34:20.100
he won't

34:20.100 --> 34:20.980
do that.

34:22.380 --> 34:23.739
No allowance equals

34:24.259 --> 34:25.420
death to me!

34:28.100 --> 34:28.739
Good point.

34:31.179 --> 34:33.659
Just say

34:34.139 --> 34:35.460
you can't reveal the source

34:35.460 --> 34:36.299
due to

34:36.819 --> 34:37.619
privacy agreements.

34:37.819 --> 34:39.219
She has no idea who you are anyway.

34:40.100 --> 34:41.659
But wouldn't

34:41.779 --> 34:42.540
that be...

34:42.699 --> 34:44.020
unfair to her?

34:46.100 --> 34:47.860
Hey, what if

34:48.619 --> 34:49.139
er...

34:49.139 --> 34:50.540
my brother still likes her?

34:51.259 --> 34:52.460
Maybe he'll see this

34:52.460 --> 34:53.339
as me playing matchmaker

34:53.500 --> 34:54.460
and be grateful!

34:54.460 --> 34:56.739
Dream on! Ten years!

34:57.020 --> 34:58.020
Seriously?

34:58.259 --> 34:59.500
You think he's been living off

34:59.500 --> 35:00.420
some high school crush?

35:00.779 --> 35:01.900
You really don't get guys at all...

35:02.219 --> 35:03.060
Well, I'm not one,

35:03.060 --> 35:04.020
so why should I?

35:12.100 --> 35:13.900
[Please proceed with your statement.]

35:22.659 --> 35:23.460
No sign of the USB

35:23.460 --> 35:24.580
at the café.

35:24.580 --> 35:26.020
Security footage

35:26.299 --> 35:27.500
doesn't help,

35:27.500 --> 35:28.580
too small to track.

35:28.980 --> 35:30.580
[At least "The Poet" confessed.]

35:30.580 --> 35:31.980
[It's over now.]

35:32.339 --> 35:33.339
[Getting groceries,]

35:33.339 --> 35:34.259
[coming to]

35:34.259 --> 35:35.380
[make hotpot!]

35:35.380 --> 35:36.940
[Let's cook away the bad vibes!]

35:58.299 --> 35:59.940
[Same old story,]

36:00.380 --> 36:01.420
[steal from]

36:01.659 --> 36:02.779
[small writers,]

36:03.219 --> 36:05.100
[pay for silence.]

36:05.659 --> 36:06.980
[This fake apology?]

36:07.299 --> 36:08.139
[Lily Vale thinks]

36:08.139 --> 36:09.179
[we're all stupid!]

36:09.940 --> 36:11.420
[Writers like this]

36:11.420 --> 36:12.739
[poison the community.]

36:13.540 --> 36:15.380
[Qianhe, step up,]

36:16.139 --> 36:17.179
[ban Lily Vale!]

36:17.659 --> 36:19.420
[Let new talent shine.]

36:20.339 --> 36:21.259
[Lily Vale out!]

36:24.739 --> 36:25.739
The Poet's account

36:25.739 --> 36:26.659
is new,

36:26.940 --> 36:27.980
no followers,

36:28.259 --> 36:29.540
minimal visibility.

36:30.460 --> 36:32.020
This level of attention...

36:33.339 --> 36:34.980
Someone's pulling strings.

36:35.580 --> 36:36.619
It's definitely Su Cheng.

36:37.380 --> 36:38.860
Classic her.

36:40.179 --> 36:41.139
When she

36:41.139 --> 36:42.940
joined Qianhe,

36:43.299 --> 36:44.819
her writing was garbage,

36:44.819 --> 36:45.420
but she pushed

36:45.420 --> 36:46.739
all the blame on her editor.

36:47.100 --> 36:48.500
Got that newbie

36:48.739 --> 36:50.259
fired from her first job!

36:51.259 --> 36:52.420
Watch out,

36:53.500 --> 36:54.100
you could be

36:54.100 --> 36:55.619
her next target!

36:56.540 --> 36:57.020
If you don't

36:57.020 --> 36:58.860
make a move...

37:02.619 --> 37:03.380
You'll be done

37:03.380 --> 37:04.739
like this hotpot meat!

37:07.380 --> 37:08.580
Who said

37:08.580 --> 37:10.060
I'm playing victim?

37:11.100 --> 37:11.980
We might

37:12.219 --> 37:13.460
not win at her game,

37:14.020 --> 37:15.020
but let's play by the rules,

37:15.699 --> 37:17.060
see how she handles that.

37:18.259 --> 37:19.100
What's the strategy?

37:19.739 --> 37:22.339
Check social media

37:22.540 --> 37:24.020
and these hashtags.

37:24.219 --> 37:25.339
All these attacks?

37:25.460 --> 37:25.980
Must be

37:25.980 --> 37:27.100
her paid trolls.

37:27.940 --> 37:29.100
For this kinda

37:29.100 --> 37:30.500
organized defamation campaign...

37:31.219 --> 37:32.739
A lawsuit for defamation sounds fair,

37:32.739 --> 37:33.420
doesn't it?

37:34.060 --> 37:34.860
Your date's

37:34.860 --> 37:36.259
coming in handy!

37:37.699 --> 37:39.299
Meeting at his firm tomorrow.

37:40.739 --> 37:41.259
Fingers crossed

37:41.259 --> 37:42.259
nothing goes wrong.

37:55.259 --> 37:55.819
Hi,

37:55.900 --> 37:57.299
I have an appointment with Mr. Liu Mao.

37:57.819 --> 37:59.339
One moment, please.

38:17.980 --> 38:19.900
[Sept. 9, 2013.]

38:20.219 --> 38:21.100
[Beautiful day.]

38:21.699 --> 38:22.940
[This moment will]

38:23.380 --> 38:24.739
[stay with me forever...]

38:25.259 --> 38:26.060
We contend that

38:26.060 --> 38:27.940
certain failure shouldn't

38:27.940 --> 38:29.659
stop us from trying.

38:29.659 --> 38:30.980
Success

38:31.259 --> 38:32.060
and failure

38:32.060 --> 38:33.259
are deeply rooted concepts

38:33.259 --> 38:35.020
in our psyche.

38:37.819 --> 38:38.540
When someone hits

38:38.540 --> 38:40.380
an unbreakable wall

38:40.380 --> 38:41.219
or faces

38:41.420 --> 38:43.380
a dead end,

38:43.580 --> 38:44.179
they might be

38:44.179 --> 38:45.580
the ones truly wrestling with

38:46.219 --> 38:47.219
our debate topic.

38:47.339 --> 38:48.819
Like our opponents.

38:49.380 --> 38:50.299
We believe

38:50.580 --> 38:52.420
sometimes letting go

38:52.420 --> 38:53.779
ends the cycle of suffering.

38:54.100 --> 38:56.259
Surrender can lead to

38:56.699 --> 38:58.060
new beginnings elsewhere.

39:37.699 --> 39:39.060
Living through

39:39.060 --> 39:41.659
endless cycles of defeat isn't living.

39:42.100 --> 39:43.420
Sometimes you need to

39:43.420 --> 39:44.339
leave that

39:44.980 --> 39:46.460
dead-end behind.

39:47.460 --> 39:48.420
Your real beginning

39:49.339 --> 39:50.619
might be

39:50.980 --> 39:52.259
just beyond it.

39:58.339 --> 39:59.259
Victory

39:59.739 --> 40:01.179
goes to

40:01.179 --> 40:02.060
the opposition!

40:06.860 --> 40:08.500
And our

40:08.500 --> 40:09.699
champion debater is,

40:10.020 --> 40:11.020
Xu Huaisong!

40:18.500 --> 40:19.139
Congrats!

40:19.819 --> 40:20.619
Thank you, Mr. Principal.

40:22.020 --> 40:22.900
Huaisong,

40:23.339 --> 40:25.020
forgetting teams,

40:25.500 --> 40:27.299
which side would you pick?

40:27.299 --> 40:28.500
Share with us.

40:32.779 --> 40:34.100
There's a line from a movie

40:34.100 --> 40:35.580
that captures it perfectly:

40:36.659 --> 40:37.940
I'll keep searching,

40:38.659 --> 40:40.139
through endless stars

40:40.139 --> 40:42.100
and fading hope,

40:42.580 --> 40:45.100
even if I must walk this path alone.

40:47.219 --> 40:47.900
Ruan Yu?

40:48.699 --> 40:49.339
Hey, Mr. Liu.

40:50.060 --> 40:50.739
Sorry for the wait.

40:50.739 --> 40:52.100
Got held up.

40:52.380 --> 40:53.940
It's fine. I was early.

40:54.420 --> 40:55.540
Let's use the conference.

40:57.900 --> 40:58.540
This way.

40:59.619 --> 41:00.380
By the way,

41:00.380 --> 41:01.020
remember that

41:01.020 --> 41:02.100
senior advisor

41:02.219 --> 41:03.540
I mentioned

41:03.659 --> 41:04.900
last time?

41:05.500 --> 41:07.179
He's in China now

41:07.179 --> 41:07.540
and

41:07.540 --> 41:08.619
really wants in

41:08.619 --> 41:09.259
on your case.

41:09.259 --> 41:10.100
So,

41:10.139 --> 41:10.860
that cool

41:10.860 --> 41:11.619
with you?

41:12.060 --> 41:12.779
No worries.

41:13.060 --> 41:13.940
Extra help

41:13.940 --> 41:15.219
is always welcome.

41:15.860 --> 41:17.259
Just so you know,

41:17.259 --> 41:18.339
he hasn't taken

41:18.339 --> 41:19.179
the Chinese bar,

41:19.179 --> 41:20.100
so he's not officially

41:20.580 --> 41:21.739
a lawyer here.

41:22.259 --> 41:23.179
We can skip this

41:23.179 --> 41:23.739
if you'd prefer...

41:23.739 --> 41:24.779
Really, it's fine.

41:26.020 --> 41:28.540
Though I have to ask,

41:28.540 --> 41:30.219
unlicensed but

41:30.259 --> 41:31.580
interested in cases?

41:32.100 --> 41:33.219
Is your big boss

41:33.540 --> 41:34.259
checking up

41:34.259 --> 41:35.100
on you guys?

41:38.060 --> 41:39.619
You might be right about that.

41:40.299 --> 41:41.179
Keeping us on our toes!

41:43.659 --> 41:44.580
After you, Ms. Ruan.

41:45.139 --> 41:45.699
Please.

41:45.699 --> 41:46.339
Thanks.

41:55.860 --> 41:56.819
Allow me to introduce...

42:41.699 --> 42:42.779
[Xu Huaisong...]

42:44.060 --> 42:45.619
[Of all people...]

43:11.739 --> 43:12.779
Tonight's going to be epic!

43:14.380 --> 43:15.540
They're planning some shows!

43:15.980 --> 43:16.540
Here!

43:22.940 --> 43:23.900
Everyone's so pumped!

43:26.580 --> 43:28.179
Over here guys!

43:41.739 --> 43:42.339
Coming!

44:03.619 --> 44:08.020
10, 9, 8, 7...

44:08.460 --> 44:11.699
6, 5, 4...

44:12.179 --> 44:16.139
3, 2, 1!
